Package moa.gui.featureanalysis

Class AttributeSelectionPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • moa.gui.featureanalysis.AttributeSelectionPanel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
    public class AttributeSelectionPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    A sub panel in visualizeFeatures tab. It shows all the attributes in a data stream so that a user selects to show the attribute's statistical information, graphs. This panel refers to weka.gui.AttributeSelectionPanel.
    Author:
    Len Trigg (trigg@cs.waikato.ac.nz), FracPete (fracpete at waikato dot ac dot nz), Yongheng Ma (2560653665@qq.com)
